{"tid":1174452,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美貿易戰】特朗普﹕期待可以達成協議","createTime":"2019-05-28T00:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T13:09:34.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"91e1a2a4c10fff4398e6f92c10dd79e9e1ca432d","tid":1174452,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T00:46:34.000Z","msg":"正在日本進行國事訪問的美國總統特朗普指出，目前美國仍未準備好與中國達成貿易協議，又指出中方可能希望試圖重啟之前的協議，並且可以達成協議，但是美國認為對中國商品關稅可以大幅上揚，並且可以非常輕鬆便可以達到。<br />\n不過特朗普仍然對中美雙方達成協議感到樂觀，認為在未來某個時間，雙方絕對可以達成理想協議，又表示期待此結果。<br />\n中國外交部發言人陸慷既指出，中方的態度始終認為中美兩國的分歧，均透過協商談判方式處理，又重申雙方的磋商要基於相互尊重及和平等互利進行。"},{"pid":"a092f9fd48c007de7f097b1ec8ad632d98bc8730","tid":1174452,"uid":133828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T01:18:26.000Z","msg":"收聲啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩到咁大重話得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0edca32bc63b0149be56ddd957f0cc66784db57","tid":1174452,"uid":171446,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T01:36:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e641a718a58264acc4cc82f8c0cc01f0aa184ecb","tid":1174452,"uid":174418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:07:23.000Z","msg":"隨時變卦"},{"pid":"951fcb0d24cb31b0732ca32823831526f1d8cce4","tid":1174452,"uid":58852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0edca32bc63b0149be56ddd957f0cc66784db57","tid":1174452,"uid":171446,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T01:36:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:09:34.000Z","msg":"正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}